This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with image segmentation. It also involves the use of deep learning, which makes it relevant to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Additionally, the use of energy maps and basins in the approach suggests that it may be related to the Neural Networks (cs.NE) category. Finally, the fact that the paper presents results on a specific dataset (Cityscapes) suggests that it may also be relevant to the Multimedia (cs.MM) category.
